# Git commit attribution

When creating commits from the agent:

- Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor`, `Made-with: Cursor`, or any Cursor/tool attribution to commit messages or PRs.
- Use plain `git commit -m` messages only — no `--trailer` flags.
- Commits should appear as the user only (Vivian Procacci / viviprocacci@gmail.com).
